org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers

Class SvhnDataFetcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers.CacheableExtractableDataSetFetcher
      • org.deeplearning4j.datasets.fetchers.SvhnDataFetcher

  • public class SvhnDataFetcher
extends CacheableExtractableDataSetFetcher
    The Street View House Numbers (SVHN) Dataset is a real-world image dataset for developing machine learning and object recognition algorithms with minimal requirement on data preprocessing and formatting. The SVHN datasets contain 10 classes (digits) with 73257 digits for training, 26032 digits for testing, and 531131 extra. Datasets in "Format 1: Full Numbers" are fetched. See: http://ufldl.stanford.edu/housenumbers/
